    {
      "id": "s001",
      "text": "Lesson 51.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "第51课。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "text": "A Pleasant Climate.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "宜人的气候。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "text": "Listen to the tape, then answer this question.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "听录音，然后回答这个问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "text": "Does it ever snow in Greece?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "希腊下过雪吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "text": "Where do you come from?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "你来自哪里？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "text": "I come from Greece.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我来自希腊。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "text": "What's the climate like in your country?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "你们国家的气候怎么样？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "text": "It's very pleasant.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "非常宜人。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "text": "What's the weather like in spring?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "春天的天气怎么样？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "text": "It's often windy in March.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "三月经常刮风。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "text": "It's always warm in April and May, but it rains sometimes.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "四月和五月总是很暖和，但有时会下雨。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "text": "What's it like in summer?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "夏天怎么样？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "text": "It's always hot in June, July, and August.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "六月、七月和八月总是很热。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "text": "The sun shines every day.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "每天都有阳光。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "text": "Is it cold or warm in autumn?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "秋天冷还是暖和？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "text": "It's always warm in September and October.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "九月和十月总是很暖和。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "text": "It's often cold in November, and it rains sometimes.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "十一月经常很冷，有时还会下雨。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "text": "Is it very cold in winter?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "冬天很冷吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "text": "It's often cold in December, January, and February.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "十二月、一月和二月经常很冷。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s020",
      "text": "It snows sometimes.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "有时会下雪。"
      }
    }
  ],
